26
00:02:11,020 --> 00:02:15,940
[The Blood of Youth: Quest of Heroic Hearts]

27
00:02:15,980 --> 00:02:18,980
[Episode 8]

28
00:02:27,960 --> 00:02:29,000
The hour of Zi...

29
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:29,560
You there.

30
00:02:29,590 --> 00:02:30,680
Come here.

31
00:02:30,840 --> 00:02:32,080
The hour of Zi...

32
00:02:32,840 --> 00:02:33,750
Come here.

33
00:02:36,750 --> 00:02:37,190
Go.

34
00:02:38,680 --> 00:02:39,150
It seems like

35
00:02:39,910 --> 00:02:41,470
we must deliver the wedding gown

36
00:02:41,750 --> 00:02:42,960
before we can meet the Divine Maiden.

37
00:02:43,310 --> 00:02:44,000
Do you remember

38
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:45,800
how we first died?

39
00:02:47,080 --> 00:02:48,560
When we entered the room, the Divine Maiden was already dead.

40
00:02:50,150 --> 00:02:50,910
This wedding gown

41
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:52,310
is like a death curse.

42
00:02:53,430 --> 00:02:54,470
Who wears white

43
00:02:55,310 --> 00:02:56,150
on their wedding gown anyway?

44
00:02:59,030 --> 00:03:00,590
But we can't possibly make another one.

45
00:03:07,080 --> 00:03:07,520
Weigui!

46
00:03:12,960 --> 00:03:14,240
We're going to need a lot of blood.

47
00:03:14,870 --> 00:03:15,560
Remember.

48
00:03:16,030 --> 00:03:16,960
We're in a dream.

49
00:03:17,470 --> 00:03:18,120
Your will

50
00:03:18,240 --> 00:03:19,800
might change certain things.

51
00:03:27,870 --> 00:03:28,430
You did it.

52
00:03:29,240 --> 00:03:29,910
You did it!

53
00:03:30,430 --> 00:03:30,840
Let's go.

54
00:03:32,660 --> 00:03:39,100
[Wedding]

55
00:03:41,310 --> 00:03:42,310
It's you.

56
00:03:43,470 --> 00:03:44,470
Divine Maiden.

57
00:03:45,630 --> 00:03:46,310
Great.

58
00:03:46,560 --> 00:03:47,190
You're alive.

59
00:03:52,680 --> 00:03:53,280
But your gown...

60
00:03:54,030 --> 00:03:54,520
How come...

61
00:03:57,150 --> 00:03:58,120
Where is the gown here?

62
00:04:05,430 --> 00:04:07,680
You disturbed my bride.

63
00:04:08,360 --> 00:04:09,680
Die!

64
00:04:16,800 --> 00:04:17,360
Wait.

65
00:04:22,430 --> 00:04:23,390
Divine Maiden.

66
00:04:23,680 --> 00:04:24,600
It's us.

67
00:04:24,920 --> 00:04:25,920
I'm Lei Lingze.

68
00:04:27,510 --> 00:04:28,160
Hush.

69
00:04:28,800 --> 00:04:30,070
You might summon the ox-head butcher.

70
00:04:37,160 --> 00:04:38,040
What are you doing here?

71
00:04:38,310 --> 00:04:39,270
We were about to ask the same thing.

72
00:04:40,070 --> 00:04:41,070
What's going on here?

73
00:04:41,600 --> 00:04:42,630
I have no idea.

74
00:04:43,270 --> 00:04:45,040
I was invited to Liuli Manor,

75
00:04:45,800 --> 00:04:47,240
but I lost consciousness.

76
00:04:50,390 --> 00:04:51,270
And I woke up

77
00:04:52,070 --> 00:04:53,600
to this wedding gown.

78
00:04:55,430 --> 00:04:56,510
We're stuck in a dream.

79
00:04:57,310 --> 00:04:58,510
It must be because of the miasma.

80
00:05:03,040 --> 00:05:03,630
I've always

81
00:05:03,950 --> 00:05:05,190
wanted to ask you this question.

82
00:05:05,920 --> 00:05:06,600
Have we

83
00:05:06,870 --> 00:05:07,680
met before?

84
00:05:11,600 --> 00:05:12,160
No.

85
00:05:12,390 --> 00:05:13,830
Now is not the time for this.

86
00:05:13,920 --> 00:05:15,070
Let's find a way to escape.

87
00:05:16,040 --> 00:05:16,750
Do you know

88
00:05:17,190 --> 00:05:19,310
any array or poison that, when combined with miasma,

89
00:05:19,560 --> 00:05:20,480
can create a dream,

90
00:05:20,720 --> 00:05:21,190
trapping

91
00:05:21,720 --> 00:05:22,720
people inside

92
00:05:23,310 --> 00:05:24,360
with no way of waking up?

93
00:05:28,830 --> 00:05:29,680
No, I don't.

94
00:05:34,560 --> 00:05:35,360
Since this is a dream,

95
00:05:36,190 --> 00:05:37,360
we just need to find a way

96
00:05:37,430 --> 00:05:38,600
to get out of the dream.

97
00:05:50,480 --> 00:05:50,750
Let's go.

98
00:06:00,830 --> 00:06:02,310
You're finally here.

99
00:06:04,000 --> 00:06:05,630
Thank you

100
00:06:05,800 --> 00:06:07,360
for finding my bride.

101
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:08,720
My love,

102
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:10,310
come to the hall with me.

103
00:06:11,950 --> 00:06:12,560
Impossible.

104
00:06:13,240 --> 00:06:14,240
If you won't marry me,

105
00:06:14,920 --> 00:06:16,720
they will die.

106
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:19,680
Divine Maiden will not marry you.

107
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:21,750
How dare you!

108
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:24,510
Lei Lingze,

109
00:06:25,040 --> 00:06:25,680
are you okay?

110
00:06:26,120 --> 00:06:26,950
Take him down.

111
00:06:27,560 --> 00:06:27,830
Let's go.

112
00:06:34,920 --> 00:06:35,720
You

113
00:06:36,870 --> 00:06:39,190
will run away from the marriage for them?

114
00:06:40,560 --> 00:06:41,560
Even if you kill me,

115
00:06:42,480 --> 00:06:43,560
I still won't let her marry you.

116
00:06:44,750 --> 00:06:45,600
Die!

117
00:06:58,600 --> 00:06:59,270
If this is a dream,

118
00:07:00,120 --> 00:07:01,480
there must be a pattern.

119
00:07:02,600 --> 00:07:04,070
I refused to go through with the wedding

120
00:07:04,510 --> 00:07:04,950
and I was killed

121
00:07:05,390 --> 00:07:06,680
by the ox-head butcher.

122
00:07:09,630 --> 00:07:10,750
It seems like in this dream,

123
00:07:11,390 --> 00:07:13,000
you must get married

124
00:07:13,270 --> 00:07:13,950
before we can leave.

125
00:07:14,040 --> 00:07:14,480
No.

126
00:07:15,270 --> 00:07:16,510
We can't let Divine Maiden

127
00:07:16,680 --> 00:07:17,750
marry a monster like that.

128
00:07:19,720 --> 00:07:20,240
When push comes to shove,

129
00:07:21,160 --> 00:07:22,160
I'll fight them.

130
00:07:22,870 --> 00:07:24,240
But our inner force is gone.

131
00:07:25,070 --> 00:07:26,190
You can't use your thunderbolt bombs

132
00:07:27,070 --> 00:07:28,040
to defend yourself either.

133
00:07:31,190 --> 00:07:31,800
Perhaps

134
00:07:33,160 --> 00:07:34,920
we can go through with the matrimonial ritual

135
00:07:34,920 --> 00:07:36,070
before we find a way to escape.

136
00:07:41,160 --> 00:07:42,360
Don't worry, Divine Maiden.

137
00:07:43,070 --> 00:07:43,480
We

138
00:07:44,120 --> 00:07:45,240
will do our best

139
00:07:45,510 --> 00:07:46,160
to protect you.

140
00:07:47,390 --> 00:07:48,430
I will be cautious too.

141
00:07:56,870 --> 00:07:58,190
Thank you

142
00:07:58,560 --> 00:08:00,070
for finding my bride.

143
00:08:00,560 --> 00:08:01,270
My love,

144
00:08:01,950 --> 00:08:03,190
come to the hall with me.

145
00:08:45,840 --> 00:08:47,960
The auspicious hour is upon us.

146
00:08:48,720 --> 00:08:50,550
Gentle light fills the hall.

147
00:08:52,150 --> 00:08:53,670
What a match

148
00:08:54,000 --> 00:08:55,670
made in heaven.

149
00:08:56,720 --> 00:08:58,840
Bride and groom,

150
00:08:59,480 --> 00:09:01,200
please hold each other's hands

151
00:09:01,630 --> 00:09:03,720
and enter this blessed hall.

152
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:07,200
First bow to Heaven and Earth.

153
00:09:09,600 --> 00:09:11,790
Second bow to your ancestors.

154
00:09:14,080 --> 00:09:16,320
Bow to each other.

155
00:09:19,240 --> 00:09:20,270
The ritual is complete.

156
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:22,960
You may now enter the bridal chamber.

157
00:09:23,150 --> 00:09:23,630
Wait.

158
00:09:26,390 --> 00:09:28,000
Right, I almost forgot about you here.

159
00:09:29,630 --> 00:09:31,320
You helped me find my bride,

160
00:09:31,630 --> 00:09:32,870
and therefore, you shall be rewarded.

161
00:09:34,440 --> 00:09:36,200
Consider the Skysplitter fragment

162
00:09:36,480 --> 00:09:37,510
your gift.

163
00:09:46,360 --> 00:09:47,630
This is the Skysplitter fragment?

164
00:09:49,440 --> 00:09:50,870
My love, let's go.

165
00:09:51,600 --> 00:09:52,150
Wait.

166
00:09:56,510 --> 00:09:57,440
We would like

167
00:09:57,670 --> 00:09:58,550
to speak with the bride.

168
00:10:00,550 --> 00:10:02,120
That depends if she

169
00:10:02,480 --> 00:10:04,030
wants to speak with you or not.

170
00:10:04,910 --> 00:10:05,720
Divine Maiden.

171
00:10:07,670 --> 00:10:08,480
Divine Maiden.

172
00:10:09,720 --> 00:10:11,320
Do you have nothing to say to us?

173
00:10:14,750 --> 00:10:15,550
Have you forgotten

174
00:10:16,440 --> 00:10:17,440
