176
00:10:20,960 --> 00:10:21,910
Enough of this.

177
00:10:22,240 --> 00:10:23,600
Or I'll have to take action.

178
00:10:24,960 --> 00:10:25,440
You...

179
00:10:25,510 --> 00:10:26,000
What's going on?

180
00:10:26,200 --> 00:10:26,750
What did you say?

181
00:10:27,320 --> 00:10:27,720
Let's go.

182
00:10:27,750 --> 00:10:28,120
Run.

183
00:10:31,270 --> 00:10:32,240
How dare you!

184
00:10:35,440 --> 00:10:36,440
You won't get away!

185
00:10:51,910 --> 00:10:52,960
How could you be so reckless

186
00:10:53,150 --> 00:10:54,510
and take that hit?

187
00:10:55,510 --> 00:10:56,320
Divine Maiden,

188
00:10:56,910 --> 00:10:57,480
forgive me.

189
00:10:58,030 --> 00:10:58,840
I won't

190
00:10:59,000 --> 00:11:00,200
be able to protect you again.

191
00:11:02,390 --> 00:11:02,870
Weigui.

192
00:11:03,670 --> 00:11:04,440
Just go.

193
00:11:05,120 --> 00:11:06,670
I'll stall them for you.

194
00:11:06,870 --> 00:11:07,390
Shut up.

195
00:11:08,360 --> 00:11:09,080
You can't die.

196
00:11:09,960 --> 00:11:10,510
Or at least,

197
00:11:10,870 --> 00:11:11,670
not here.

198
00:11:13,510 --> 00:11:14,960
Now's not the time for this.

199
00:11:15,320 --> 00:11:15,750
Let's go.

200
00:11:17,510 --> 00:11:18,510
The most dangerous place

201
00:11:18,550 --> 00:11:19,510
is the safest place.

202
00:11:19,550 --> 00:11:19,870
Let's go.

203
00:11:21,150 --> 00:11:21,480
Let's go.

204
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:31,200
This is...

205
00:11:31,480 --> 00:11:32,720
Where we always wake up.

206
00:11:37,840 --> 00:11:39,480
How can we escape from this dream?

207
00:11:51,750 --> 00:11:53,630
[Death is Life]

208
00:11:53,630 --> 00:11:55,030
Death is life?

209
00:11:56,120 --> 00:11:56,870
What does it mean?

210
00:12:01,790 --> 00:12:02,550
Could this be

211
00:12:03,030 --> 00:12:04,480
