215
00:12:15,390 --> 00:12:16,120
No way.

216
00:12:16,670 --> 00:12:18,150
Weigui and I died several times.

217
00:12:18,960 --> 00:12:20,000
But we never woke up from the dream.

218
00:12:26,030 --> 00:12:26,750
In those times,

219
00:12:27,240 --> 00:12:28,670
