225
00:12:51,270 --> 00:12:52,000
After you.

226
00:13:32,640 --> 00:13:36,320
♪How can I make peace when time♪

227
00:13:36,680 --> 00:13:39,440
♪Only leaves me with my shadow?♪

228
00:13:40,880 --> 00:13:44,400
♪Yet the intertwining bonds in my life♪

229
00:13:44,600 --> 00:13:47,680
♪Render me blind♪

230
00:13:49,080 --> 00:13:52,600
♪I was once naive and innocent♪

231
00:13:53,000 --> 00:13:55,880
♪Seeking a soul with whom to dance♪

232
00:13:57,040 --> 00:14:00,840
♪Yet my life is like a wisp of smoke♪

233
00:14:01,000 --> 00:14:04,000
♪Scattered by a gust of wind♪

234
00:14:04,280 --> 00:14:07,000
♪In this life, I am not destined to be understood♪

235
00:14:07,320 --> 00:14:09,280
♪But misunderstood♪

236
00:14:09,440 --> 00:14:12,360
♪I do not know sincerity♪

237
00:14:12,520 --> 00:14:17,120
♪If the river of time could flow back to its starting point♪

238
00:14:17,280 --> 00:14:20,440
♪Let's not meet again♪

239
00:14:20,600 --> 00:14:23,400
♪No one will be able to understand me♪

240
00:14:23,800 --> 00:14:25,480
♪None will go as I wish♪

241
00:14:25,800 --> 00:14:28,720
♪How I long for that one moment to last forever♪

242
00:14:28,840 --> 00:14:33,440
♪All mortal obsessions turn into dusts of nothingness♪

243
00:14:33,720 --> 00:14:36,640
♪Let's not meet in another life♪

244
